TaggingRules->{
 "ModificationHighlight" -> False, "ColorType" -> "", "LinkTrails" -> "", 
  "ExampleCounter" -> 1, 
  "Openers" -> {
   "PrimaryExamplesSection" -> Open, "ExampleSection" -> {"0" -> Open}, 
    "AllOptsTable" -> Closed}, "NewStyles" -> True, 
  "CitationPopupData" -> $Failed, "ShowCitation" -> False, "HasOptions" -> 
  True, "RootCaptions" -> "", "HeaderCoreAreaLink" -> {}, 
  "Metadata" -> {
   "built" -> "{2026, 4, 12, 17, 57, 47.007440}", 
    "history" -> {"14.2", "", "", ""}, "context" -> "QuantumMob`Q3`", 
    "keywords" -> {}, "specialkeywords" -> {}, 
    "tutorialcollectionlinks" -> {}, "index" -> True, "label" -> 
    "Quantum Mob/ Q3 Symbol", "language" -> "en", "paclet" -> "QuantumMob/Q3",
     "status" -> "None", "summary" -> 
    "RowInsertion[wt, a] returns a new Weyl tableau with integer a added to \
Weyl tableau wt by the row insertion process. RowInsertion[wt, {a1, a2, ..., \
a n}] successively add integers a1, a2, ..., an. RowInsertion[{p, q}, {a, b}] \
returns new pair of Weyl tableaux with integers a and b added to the \
recording Weyl tableaux p (tracking the order of insertions) and insertion \
Weyl tableau q (containing the inserted entries), respectively, where a is \
the ordering index and b is the content index. RowInsertion[{p, q}, {{a1, a2, \
..., a n}, {b1, b2, ..., b n}}] successively add integer pairs {a1, b1}, {a2, \
b2}, ..., {an, bn}. RowInsertion[{p, q}, {Automatic, {b1, b2, ..., bn}}] is \
equivalent to RowInsertion[{p, q}, {{1, 2, ..., n}, {b1, b2, ..., bn}}].", 
    "synonyms" -> {}, "tabletags" -> {}, "title" -> "RowInsertion", 
    "titlemodifier" -> "", "metadescription" -> "", "windowtitle" -> 
    "RowInsertion", "type" -> "Symbol", "uri" -> 
    "QuantumMob/Q3/ref/RowInsertion"}},
